reviewText: Hi,  This is a rare concert DVD, there are not many from Roxette,  how sad !  Anyway, the video quality is not true DVD quality, seems like a  " B + "  video & sound  grade transfer to DVD.  But as said, there are not many to begin with, so I am VERY HAPPY with this one !!!  No DVD extras.  GREAT price & very hard to find too !!!  A very fun & engoyable concert DVD !!!
